  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was designed to estimate the effect of two-year treatment with time-released
      garlic-based drug Allicor on the progression of carotid atherosclerosis in double-blinded
      placebo-controlled randomized clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
